quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  42,51,"Kisi bashar (Insaan) ka yeh muqaam nahin hai ke Allah us se ru-baru baat karey, uski baat ya to wahee (isharey/ revelation) ke taur par hoti hai, ya purday ke piche se, ya phir woh koi paigaambar (farishta) bhejta hai aur woh uske hukum se jo kuch woh chahta hai, wahi karta hai. Woh bartar aur Hakeem(wise) hai"
  42,52,"Aur isi tarah (aey Muhammad s.a.s) humne apne hukum se ek rooh tumhari tarf wahee ki hai. Tumhein kuch pata na tha ke kitaab kya hoti hai aur Imaan kya hota hai, Magar us rooh ko humne ek roshni bana diya jissey hum raah dikhate hain apne bandon mein se jisey chahte hain. Yaqeenan tum seedhey raaste ki taraf rehnumayi kar rahey ho"
  42,53,"Us khuda ke raaste ki taraf jo zameen aur aasmaano ki har cheez ka maalik hai. khabardar raho, saarey muaamlaat Allah hi ki taraf rujoo karte hain"
  43,1,Haa Meem
  43,2,Kasam hai is wazeh kitaab ki
  43,3,Ke humne isey arabi zubaan ka Quran banaya hai taa-ke tumlog isey samjho
  43,4,"Aur dar haqeeqat yeh ummul kitaab mein sabt(transcribed) hai, hamare haan badi buland maratba aur hikmat se labrez kitaab"
  43,5,Ab kya hum tumse bezaar hokar yeh dars-e-naseehat tumhare yahan bhejna chodh dein sirf isliye tum hadd se guzare huey log ho
  43,6,Pehle guzri hui qaumon mein bhi baarha (baar baar) humne Nabi bheje hain
  43,7,Kabhi aisa nahin hua ke koi Nabi unke haan (yahan) aaya ho aur unhon ne uska mazak na udaya ho
  43,8,Phir jo log insey badarja zyada taaqatwar thay unhein humne halak kardiya. Pichli qaumon ki misalien guzar chuki hain
  43,9,Agar tum in logon se pucho ke zameen aur aasmaano ko kisne paida kiya hai to yeh khud kahenge ke inhein usi zabardast ilmi hasti ne paida kiya hai
  43,10,Wahi na jisne tumhare liye is zameen ko gehwara (cradle) banaya aur ismein tumhari khatir raaste bana diye taa-ke tum apni manzil e maqsood ki raah paa sako
  43,11,Jisne ek khaas miqdar mein aasman se paani utara aur uske zariye se murda (dead) zameen ko jila uthaya. Isi tarah ek roz tum zameen se baramad kiye jaogey
  43,12,"Wahi jisne yeh tamaam jodey (pairs) paida kiye, aur jisne tumhare liye kashtiyon (ships) aur jaanwaron ko sawari banaya taa-ke tum unki pusht (backs) par chadho"
  43,13,Aur jab unpar baitho (sit) to apne Rubb ka ehsan yaad karo aur kaho ke “paak hai woh jisne hamare liye in cheezon ko musakkhar(bas mein) kardiya warna hum unhein qaabu mein laane ki taaqat na rakhte thay
  43,14,Aur ek roz humein apne Rubb ki taraf palatna hai”
  43,15,"(Yeh sab kuch jaante aur maante huey bhi) in logon ne uske bandon (servants) mein se baaz ko uska juz (part) bana daala, haqeeqat yeh hai ke Insaan khula ehsan faramosh hai"
  43,16,Kya Allah ne apni makhlooq mein se apne liye betiyan intikhab (chose) ki aur tumhein beiton (sons) se nawaza
  43,17,Aur haal yeh hai ke jis aulad ko yeh log us khuda e Rehman ki taraf mansoob karte hain uski wiladat ka musda (tidings/news/khabar) jab khud in mein se kisi ko diya jata hai to uske mooh par siyahi(darkens) chaa jaati hai aur woh gham se bhar jaata hai
  43,18,Kya Allah ke hisse mein woh aulad aayi jo zewaron (ornaments) mein paali jaati hai aur behas o hujjat mein apna mudda puri tarah wazeh bhi nahin kar sakti
  43,19,"Unhon ne farishton ko, jo khuda e Rehman ke khaas banday hain, auratein karar de liya. Kya unke jism ki saakht inhon ne dekhi hai? Inki gawahi likh li jayegi aur inhein iske jawab-dahi karni hogi"
  43,20,"Yeh kehte hain “agar khuda-e-Rehman chahta (ke hum unki ibadat na karein) to hum kabhi unko na poojte” yeh is maamle ki haqeeqat ko qatai nahin jaante, mehaz teer tukkay ladate hain (are simply conjecturing /guess work)"
  43,21,"Kya humne issey pehle koi kitaab inko di thi jiski sanad [apne is malaika (farihste) parasti ke liye] yeh apne paas rakhte hon"
  43,22,"Nahin, balke yeh kehte hain ke humne apne baap dada ko ek tarike par paya hai aur hum unhi ke nakshe qadam par chal rahe hain"
  43,23,"Isi tarah tumse pehle jis basti mein bhi humne koi nazeer(darane wala) bheja, uske khaate peete logon ne yahi kaha ke humne apne baap dada ko ek tareeqe par paya hai aur hum unhi ke naqshe qadam ki pairwi kar rahe hain"